<% layout("/layouts/boilerplate") %>
<h1>Exciting Events</h1>
<h2>Insightful Workshop</h2>
<br />
<div class="main">
  <div class="events">
    <div class="event-pic"><img src="../images/download (1).jpeg" /></div>
    <div class="event-text">
      <h2>Sensors</h2>
      <p>
        Step into the world where machines feel their surroundings! The Robotics
        Club of NIT Bhopal presents an immersive Sensors Workshop, designed to
        introduce you to the eyes, ears, and touch of robotics. From motion
        detection to temperature sensing, light tracking to ultrasonic range
        finding—discover how sensors gather real-world data and make autonomous
        systems smarter. Through hands-on experiments and real-time interfacing,
        you'll learn how to connect and program various sensors with
        microcontrollers to create interactive and intelligent projects. Whether
        you're building a line-following robot or a weather station, this
        workshop is your gateway to making tech truly responsive.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="events">
    <div class="event-text">
      <h2>Microcontrollers</h2>
      <p>
        Curious about what powers modern tech—from robots to smart devices? The
        Robotics Club of NIT Bhopal invites you to an engaging Microcontrollers
        Workshop, where you’ll dive into the brains behind the bots! Learn how
        microcontrollers like Arduino and ESP32 bring machines to life through
        sensors, code, and clever circuitry. Whether you're a beginner or a
        tinkerer looking to level up, this hands-on workshop will equip you with
        the skills to build, program, and control real-world projects. Get ready
        to explore the magic of embedded systems and unlock a whole new
        dimension of innovation. Let’s get wired and inspired!
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="event-pic"><img src="../images/download (1).jpeg" /></div>
  </div>
  <div class="events">
    <div class="event-pic"><img src="../images/download (1).jpeg" /></div>
    <div class="event-text">
      <h2>Cadathon</h2>
      <p>
        Ready to bring your ideas to life? The Robotics Club of NIT Bhopal
        presents an exciting CAD Workshop that’s all about turning imagination
        into innovation! Whether you're dreaming of designing sleek robots,
        futuristic machines, or smart mechanical systems, this is your gateway
        to mastering the art of Computer-Aided Design. Dive into the world where
        creativity meets precision, and learn how to sketch, model, and simulate
        like a pro. No prior experience? No worries! Our hands-on sessions and
        expert mentors will guide you every step of the way. Join us and start
        shaping the future—one design at a time!
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="events">
    <div class="event-text">
      <h2>Hardware Interfacing</h2>
      <p>
        Ever wondered how robots sense, move, and interact with the world around
        them? The Robotics Club of NIT Bhopal brings you an exciting Hardware
        Interfacing Workshop, where theory meets hands-on action! Dive into the
        fundamentals of connecting microcontrollers with sensors, actuators, and
        other electronic components to build responsive and intelligent systems.
        From blinking LEDs to controlling motors and reading sensor data, you'll
        learn how to make hardware and code work together seamlessly. Perfect
        for beginners and enthusiasts alike, this workshop is your stepping
        stone into the world of embedded electronics and robotics. Let’s bridge
        the gap between code and circuits!
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="event-pic"><img src="../images/download (1).jpeg" /></div>
  </div>
  <div class="last">And Much More</div>
</div>
